#: classes/spider.class.php:34
msgid ""
"Spider Analyser是一款用于跟踪WordPress网站各种搜索引擎蜘蛛爬行日志的插件，并"
"进行详细的蜘蛛爬行数据统计、蜘蛛行为分析、蜘蛛爬取分析及伪蜘蛛拦截等。"
msgstr ""
"Spider Analyser is a WordPress plugin for tracking various search engine "
"spider crawl logs, and detailed spider crawl data statistics, spider "
"behavior analysis, spider crawl analysis and false spider block."

